          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript is a compendium of various rites and observances (vratas) and is a manual for those performed at the beginning of each cycle (season) of four months (cāturmāsya) of the year and includes rites of fasting (vrata), bathing, and others. There is a table of contents at the beginning of the manuscript (Part 1, f. 1-3).</summary>
